rows.label: qst201408_msg0001
rows.name: Hey! Silence!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0002
rows.name:
You have disturbed the royal
slumber. This we cannot forgive,
even if you are way cute.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0003
rows.name:
It's really not good for your looks
to stay up like this! For our sake,
why don't you go to bed yourselves?

rows.label: qst201408_msg0004
rows.name: Rinne!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0005
rows.name:
Hikari and I are trying to settle
who's got the most Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0006
rows.name:
We really think you ought to have
included us from the start. But
it sounds fun, nevertheless!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0007
rows.name:
We want you to judge which one of
us has the most Girl Power, Rinne.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0008
rows.name:
Very well! We will
oversee your contest!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0023
rows.name:
Okay. Let's get down to it. Let's
talk about who we're into.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0024
rows.name:
Wow, that really is all
you think about...

rows.label: qst201408_msg0009
rows.name:
So. Rinne. Tell us what qualities
your ideal man would have.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0010
rows.name:
Yeah, I mean, you only like girls. So I'd
be interested to hear what kind of guy
you'd be into, if you were, that is.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0011
rows.name:
Well, we suppose that a man
must be financially solvent.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0012
rows.name: Financially solvent?

rows.label: qst201408_msg0013
rows.name: Yes. Who likes to share?

rows.label: qst201408_msg0014
rows.name:
But of course, we imagine
there are other vital traits.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0015
rows.name:
If we were interested, excellent
manners and breeding would be a must.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0016
rows.name:
For example, he'd need to know how
to serve tea, scrub a bathtub, and
have a nice villa by the lake.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0017
rows.name: Don't you think that's a little...

rows.label: qst201408_msg0018
rows.name:
That's a lot, Rinne! You're really
setting the bar high for us girls!

rows.label: qst201408_msg0019
rows.name:
It's just as well that we prefer
girls. The man who'd meet our
requirements would be a rare creature.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0020
rows.name:
We've not really managed to
talk up a storm so far...

rows.label: qst201408_msg0021
rows.name:
Well, maybe we haven't had
the best partners so far.

rows.label: qst201408_msg0022
rows.name: I'm sure the next one will be better!
